Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.91,0:06:46.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它打算一口氣解決我們
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.32,0:06:50.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.95,0:06:56.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣  誰都別想來妨礙我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.29,0:06:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論是誰  都休想
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.62,0:07:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴上同學
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.74,0:07:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.04,0:07:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.88,0:07:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能和大家打架啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.02,0:07:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菜菜子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.21,0:07:24.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁現在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.75,0:07:41.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菜菜子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.86,0:07:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別過來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.60,0:07:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.90,0:08:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.79,0:08:26.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.93,0:08:31.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還給我  快還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.93,0:08:33.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.81,0:08:35.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.85,0:08:36.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擅自地…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.00,0:08:39.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動了起來熊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.35,0:08:57.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個孩子要由我來拯救
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.90,0:08:58.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.85,0:09:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠  請救救菜菜子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.15,0:09:17.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學長快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.34,0:09:35.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃龍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.04,0:09:48.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  身體能動了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.57,0:10:01.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得…得救了熊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.04,0:10:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.21,0:10:08.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.48,0:10:12.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我…  由我來拯救
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.64,0:10:13.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會再讓你肆意妄為了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.66,0:10:30.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機會來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.33,0:10:47.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shadow的暴走停不下來啊熊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.74,0:11:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菜菜子  菜菜子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.99,0:11:39.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菜菜子  振作點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.85,0:11:42.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明沒有受傷  但她好像很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.67,0:11:44.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是這個地方的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.07,0:11:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點把她帶到外面去吧熊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.23,0:11:47.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
